"title": "5776: achievement",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5776: achievement",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Human beings can achieve many things, though any achievement which disregards God is futile. God always achieves what he intends. Anything of eternal value needs God-given resources.</p>\n<h2>Kinds of human achievement</h2>\n<h3>Accumulation of wealth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:4\">EST 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:23\">1KI 10:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:22\">2CH 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:26-1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:26–10:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:27\">2CH 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:12\">JOB 42:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:4-Eccl2:9\">ECC 2:4–2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Political power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:41-Gen41:43\">GEN 41:41–41:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:21\">1KI 4:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:26\">2CH 9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:1\">EST 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth10:2-Esth10:3\">EST 10:2–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37-Dan2:38\">DAN 2:37–2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:48\">DAN 2:48</a></p>\n<h3>Buildings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:1-1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:1–7:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:30\">DAN 4:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:1\">MRK 13:1</a></p>\n<h3>Great learning</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:32-1Kgs4:34\">1KI 4:32–4:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:13-Eccl1:16\">ECC 1:13–1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:17\">DAN 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Military victory</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:14-Gen14:16\">GEN 14:14–14:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:8-Exod17:13\">EXO 17:8–17:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:24-Josh8:26\">JOS 8:24–8:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:14-Judg4:16\">JDG 4:14–4:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:7\">1SA 18:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:35-2Sam22:43\">2SA 22:35–22:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:34-Ps18:42\">PSA 18:34–18:42</a></p>\n<h3>Acts of courage</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:6-1Sam14:14\">1SA 14:6–14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:50\">1SA 17:50</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:8-2Sam23:21\">2SA 23:8–23:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:11-1Chr11:23\">1CH 11:11–11:23</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual achievements</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:19\">ROM 15:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:17\">LUK 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:12\">JHN 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">ACT 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:26-Acts20:27\">ACT 20:26–20:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:1-2Cor3:3\">2CO 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:13-1John2:14\">1JN 2:13–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:19\">REV 2:19</a></p>\n<h2>Limitations of human achievements</h2>\n<h3>Human achievements can lead to pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:12-Isa10:15\">ISA 10:12–10:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:10-Deut8:18\">DEU 8:10–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:16\">2CH 26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:29-Dan4:30\">DAN 4:29–4:30</a></p>\n<h3>Human achievements can give false security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:20\">LUK 12:16–12:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:11-2Kgs19:13\">2KI 19:11–19:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:11-Isa37:13\">ISA 37:11–37:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:21-2Kgs19:28\">2KI 19:21–19:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:21-Isa37:29\">ISA 37:21–37:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:7\">JER 48:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:7-Rev18:8\">REV 18:7–18:8</a></p>\n<h3>Human achievements are ultimately futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:11\">ECC 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:6\">PSA 39:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17-Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:17–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6\">ISA 40:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:13\">HAB 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Human achievements do not lead to justification</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:39\">ACT 13:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">ROM 5:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:15-Gal2:16\">GAL 2:15–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:21\">GAL 2:21</a></p>\n<h2>God can thwart human achievements</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:1-Gen11:9\">GEN 11:1–11:9</a></strong> <em>God will overthrow all human achievement that is in opposition to him.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:12\">JOB 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:10\">PSA 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:19\">ISA 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:10\">REV 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:16-Rev18:19\">REV 18:16–18:19</a></p>\n<h2>God's achievements</h2>\n<h3>God's purposes are always accomplished</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:10\">ISA 46:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:2\">JOB 42:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:24\">ISA 14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:20\">JER 23:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:24\">JER 30:24</a></p>\n<h3>Creation as God's achievement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:24\">PSA 104:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:2-Ps104:23\">PSA 104:2–104:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:25-Isa40:26\">ISA 40:25–40:26</a></p>\n<h3>Salvation as God's achievement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:28\">JHN 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:30\">JHN 19:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">ACT 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:14\">HEB 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual resources for human achievements</h2>\n<h3>Achieving things with God's help</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1\">PSA 127:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:30\">2SA 22:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:29\">PSA 18:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:5\">2CH 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6-Zech4:9\">ZEC 4:6–4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:5\">JHN 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:18-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:6\">1CO 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:13\">PHP 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:13\">PHP 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Achieving things by faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:23\">MRK 9:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">MAT 17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:21\">MAT 21:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:22-Mark11:23\">MRK 11:22–11:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:6\">LUK 17:6</a></p>\n<h3>Achieving things through prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13-John14:14\">JHN 14:13–14:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:27\">1SA 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16-Jas5:18\">JAS 5:16–5:18</a></p>\n<h3>Achievements out of trials and sorrows</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:4\">ROM 5:3–5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:10\">2CO 7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:7–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:4\">JAS 1:2–1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Achieving things with the help of fellow believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:2\">GAL 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42-Acts2:45\">ACT 2:42–2:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:37\">ACT 4:32–4:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12-Acts5:16\">ACT 5:12–5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:13-Phil4:14\">PHP 4:13–4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:18\">PHP 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24-Heb10:25\">HEB 10:24–10:25</a></p>",
